ll\"><div id=\"panel-3702-0-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Beaverton branch of the American Automobile Association providing members with Emergency Roadside Service, Travel Services, Insurance &amp; Retail Travel Store.</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-3702-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-3702-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3702-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3755\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/advanced-camera.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/advanced-camera.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/advanced-camera-100x73.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/advanced-camera-150x109.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/advanced-camera-200x145.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/advanced-camera-280x203.jpg 280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-3702-1-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3702-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><h2><strong>Advance Camera Inc</strong></h2>\n<p><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--white\">Dave Sleeth&nbsp; 8124 SW Beaverton Hillsdale Hwy&nbsp; Portland, OR 97225 </span></p>\n<p><strong>Phone:</strong> 503 292-6996&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Fax:</strong> 503-449-5848</p>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-3702-1-2\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3702-1-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"5\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p>We offer <a href=\"https://www.advancecamera.com/repair\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--custom\">repair services</span></a> on film and digital photography gear! Our technicians have been trained to work on a variety of photographic gear, such as lenses, flashes, camera bodies, binoculars, tripods, etc. We have technicians who have extensive experience and training for working on cameras from companies like Pentax, Mamiya, Leica, Canon, Nikon, Minolta, Fujica, Hasselblad, and the list goes on.</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-3702-2\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-3702-2-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3702-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"6\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p><a href=\"https://www.apmortgage.com/michelle-zafiris\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3763\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/american-pacific.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/american-pacific.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/american-pacific-150x150.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/american-pacific-100x100.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/american-pacific-200x200.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/american-pacific-280x280.jpg 280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-3702-2-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3702-2-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"7\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><h2 class=\"branch-manager__heading\" role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"1\" data-uw-rm-heading=\"level\">American Pacific Mortgage</h2>\n<p class=\"branch-manager__subheading\">Reverse Mortgage Loan Officer • Portland Branch • NMLS #1644012</p>\n<p class=\"branch-manager__heading\" role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"1\" data-uw-rm-heading=\"level\">Michelle Zafiris 2737 SE 21st. Ave, Portland, OR 97202</p>\n<div class=\"branch-manager__phone\">\n<div class=\"branch-manager__phone__item\">\n<div class=\"sr-only-clip\">Phone number&nbsp;&nbsp;503.754.7088</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-3702-2-2\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3702-2-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"8\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p><span id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_module_14265380554691154\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"rich_text\">I am committed to helping my clients live the life they choose with dignity and security. As a Certified Senior Advisor (CSA®), I am specially trained to understand the aging process—how it impacts health, finances, decision making, and overall quality of life. This holistic perspective allows me to guide clients through the complexities of retirement with both clarity and compassion.</span></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\t"
